为我的无知和傲慢而造成的！！！！！我现在努力学习，可我有时候发现现在努力得太晚了。过去所犯下的错误，能补救回来吗？<br><br>所以我不是有过自杀的想法，而是经常有，现在也有。","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/03/54/35406.jpg","floor":"#33-1","id":"1510467","time":"2019-10-15 22:42","userId":"35406","userName":"又见骷髅","userSign":"","message":"永远没有太晚这件事！<br>加油我们一起一步步从底层往上攀登！"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/05/84/58462.jpg","floor":"#33-2","id":"1510799","time":"2019-10-16 14:02","userId":"linali","userName":"李梦眠","userSign":"","message":"有目标有动力 终究会越来越好的。"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/33/58/335863.jpg","floor":"#34","id":"1510405","time":"2019-10-15 21:54","userId":"335863","userName":"久我酒红","userSign":"(我们将在没有黑暗的地方相见)","message":"1，17岁自杀未遂过","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/24/22/242277.jpg","floor":"#35","id":"1510426","time":"2019-10-15 22:09","userId":"242277","userName":"DDpzj","userSign":"(要是种崎敦美或桑原由气宣布结婚我就声豚毕业 ... ...)","message":"思考自我的时候是1，觉得自己没有价值啊，活着又那么痛苦<br>然后思考死亡的时候是0，我太怕死了，我从小学时候开始怕死怕了十几年了","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/39/51/395198.jpg","floor":"#36","id":"1510431","time":"2019-10-15 22:14","userId":"395198","userName":"笑颜の行方","userSign":"","message":"0","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/31/34/313469.jpg","floor":"#37","id":"1510453","time":"2019-10-15 22:30","userId":"313469","userName":"Cedar","userSign":"(｡´-д-)","message":"110<br><a href=\"https://bgm.tv/group/topic/353072\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">隔壁帖子</a>被关闭了喔","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/33/71/337184.jpg","floor":"#38","id":"1510455","time":"2019-10-15 22:32","userId":"337184","userName":"haveatry","userSign":"(我们遇到什么 DD , 也不要怕 , 顶着面对它 , 消除单推 ...)","message":"这么感兴趣的吗？","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/03/54/35406.jpg","floor":"#39","id":"1510465","time":"2019-10-15 22:40","userId":"35406","userName":"又见骷髅","userSign":"(自nue)","message":"0 自杀就是磨灭了一切可能性","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/34/26/342667.jpg